# Supplier Shortlist — EXP-20260630-007 — Agarbatti Incense Sticks to Fiji

## RFQ facts from screenshot/source
- Source: go4WorldBusiness buy lead 1304702 — https://go4worldbusiness.com/inquiries/send/buyleads/1304702/wanted--agarbatti-incense-sticks
- Product: Agarbatti / incense sticks
- Quantity: 1 Ton/Tons
- Buyer country/destination: Fiji
- Payment terms shown: T/T
- Shipping terms shown: FOB or CIF
- Contact visible: Vasu Amin
- Date shown: Jun-15-26
- Marketplace badge: Verified

## Recommendation
Pursue as a low-risk supplier-quote pass, not yet as a quote-ready buyer deal. Buyer company identity, import credentials, exact spec/packing/fragrance, destination port, and advance payment willingness must be checked before sending a final buyer quote.

## Supplier candidates found
| Priority | Supplier | Location | Why shortlisted | Source |
|---:|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | Megha Incenses / Megha Aromatics | New Delhi | Public site says wholesale/export, since 1952, incense/dhoop/cones/oils; buyer enquiries welcome; 20+ countries. Good closest/NCR option. | https://meghaincenses.com/contact/ |
| 2 | Divinity Industries | New Delhi | TradeIndia page lists GST, address in Karol Bagh, business type manufacturer/supplier, and bulk Agarbatti/Reed Diffuser/Potpourri products. | https://www.tradeindia.com/divinity-industries-1273690/agarbatti.html |
| 3 | Indian Agarbathi Manufacturers | Bengaluru, Karnataka | Public site lists GST, Bengaluru address, incense sticks exporter/supplier/manufacturer. | https://www.indianagarbatti.co.in/contact-us.html |
| 4 | Melting Aromas | Bangalore, Karnataka | Public site positions itself as incense sticks manufacturer/supplier; contact page lists exports email and Bangalore address. | https://meltingaromas.in/contact/ |
| 5 | Ashic Agarbatti | Sivakasi, Tamil Nadu | Public contact page lists export positioning, office in Sivakasi, minimum LCL/FCL quantities and export countries. | https://ashicagarbatti.com/contact-us/ |
| 6 | Sudhersen Exports | Tindivanam / Villupuram, Tamil Nadu | IndiaMART exporter directory snippet shows incense agarbatti sticks at around ₹60/kg and 12-year listing; verify export docs/capacity. | https://dir.indiamart.com/impcat/agarbatti.html?biz=20 |
| 7 | Ekikrut Exports India Pvt Ltd | Pune, Maharashtra | IndiaMART exporter directory shows wood metallic rose premium agarbatti/incense sticks and exporter-style company name; verify capacity. | https://dir.indiamart.com/impcat/agarbatti.html?biz=20 |
| 8 | Jai Neelkanth Agarbatti | Ahmedabad, Gujarat | ExportersIndia page lists verified seller with premium incense sticks. Useful western India backup. | https://www.exportersindia.com/indian-suppliers/incense-sticks.htm |
| 9 | Sanflourish Industries Pvt Ltd | Satara, Maharashtra | ExportersIndia page lists raw/white/five-in-one incense sticks with GST/trusted status; verify finished export packing. | https://www.exportersindia.com/indian-suppliers/incense-sticks.htm |
| 10 | Anubhav Incense Manufacturing Company | Bengaluru, Karnataka | ExportersIndia page lists verified Bangalore incense manufacturer, sandalwood/flora products; likely higher price/premium segment. | https://www.exportersindia.com/indian-suppliers/incense-sticks.htm |

## RFQ to send suppliers
Ask for quote for 1,000 kg agarbatti/incense sticks for export to Fiji, FOB India port and CIF Fiji option, with: fragrance options, stick length, sticks/pack, master carton details, gross/net weight, MOQ, lead time, IEC/GST, export docs, MSDS/COA if available, fumigation/packing declaration, payment terms, quote validity, and product photos.

## Guardrails
- Supplier quote outreach is standing-authorized, but no buyer quotation/final price/Incoterms/origin/HSN commitment yet.
- Candidate HSN/ITC-HS to verify later: likely 3307.41 for agarbatti/odoriferous preparations operating by burning; do not treat as final classification.

